#matplotlib
use pyenv - pyenv activate mypenv..
possible new setup using `env PYTHON_CONFIGURE_OPTS="--enable-framework CC=clang" pyenv virtualenv 2.7.8 xxx` should also work


#tensorflow

to separate inference from train model - 
1. add checkpoint
2. create two separate graphs a) train and b) inference
3. after training use checkpoint to initialize inference graph
4. save inference graph.
